title: Evil Robot 1.0.5.apk
description:
An Experiment carried out by a Mad Scientist to make world most powerful TERROR MACHINE has finally completed. He has completed his first Evil Robot successfully. You are the only one who could pilot this Evil Robot.
Military will try to defeat you,kill then all,Level the ground with your fury and show no mercy.Lots of games to become a Hero. Come be a Super Villain for the first time...
Evil Robot
is comming...
Features
--------------
1. Breathtaking Graphics
Experience the action in stunning graphics! Witness the dazzling display of Robot's unique skills!
2. Collection of orbs! 
Beautiful orbs with extreme power will be parachuted!
3. Endless Fun! 
An endless game is much more fun than ending,Kill and move as far as possible with these heavy terror machine!
4. Rocking Guns 
Unleash your Robo fury with our 50Caliber guns, Rocket Launchers and Laser Shots!
